summary:
New player home up date.
This is a revisit to my Home To Let 2.
descriptionHtml:
[u][b]Sorry but i am no longer supporting this mod, so feel free to use it how you wish.[/b][/u]


New player home up date.


Lyra is away from home and has left it in your hands, so look after it and have fun.

This is a revisit to my Home To Let 2, a no loaddoor home near Ivarstead. Its a small but well equipped abode now with stable and horse. I have also added a bridge over the river for better access.

I use this in my own game and I made it to fit my needs. it is not a home to get lost in, it is for somone who wants to craft, store and play the game not the house.


As a no load door home it will rain inside, and the mannequins do not always behave.

Note: if you are updating from Home To Let 2 I have made some changes to the inside storage so move your items to the Dwemer chest on the right as you come in the door.
author: Ronnin47
